text: @realmoney one timer! Dec 16, 2020 | 09:07 AM EST DOUG KASS Is Mr. Market Secretariat or a Cheap 'Tuesday Night' Horse? * Rosy Scenario has taken over the investment playing field "as price has a way of changing sentiment" (hat tip to Divine Ms. M) * Unprecedented liquidity,
